FBIS4-16174 "drsov072_a_94018" FBIS-SOV-94-072 Daily Report 13 Apr 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Yeltsin Wraps Up Spain Visit in Barcelona 13 Apr Yeltsin Wraps Up Spain Visit in Barcelona 13 Apr LD1304130694 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1210 GMT 13 Apr 94 LD1304130694 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [By ITAR-TASS special correspondents Lyudmila Aleksandrova, Nikita Yermakov, Yuriy Sizov and Vladimir Shekhovtsov] [Text] Barcelona April 13 TASS -- Russian President Boris Yeltsin arrived in the Catalonian capital of Barcelona today morning. This is the second lap of his official visit to Spain. At the Barcelona international airport the head of the Russian state was welcomed by Jordi Pujol, chairman of the Catalonian autonomous government, and other officials. At Hotel "Juan Carlos 1" Yeltsin met the directorate of the Barcelona hospital, where he was operated in 1990. He thanked the Barcelona physicians for the medical aid given him at that time.
